Corrosion behavior of zinc anode can be investigated via Tafel experiments. Then, the polarization method can be used for obtaining the corrosion parameters. The zinc anode was scanned over a range of potential in the electrolytes. The relation between potential and logarithm of current density can be expressed, as given in Eq. 4:4η=2.3RTαFlogi−2.3RTαFlogi0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
